Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無限的時間將跳動停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們悄聲無息地燃燒著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有任何人注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界已經脫軌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被紅世之火所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------------------OP-----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:25.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そして　この空　赤く染めて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:31.63,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}また来る時　この一身で　進むだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:48.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}すれ違っていく‘人’も　紛れ失くした‘モノ’も
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:53.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつかは　消えゆく記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:00:59.54,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}熱く揺るがす‘強さ’　儚く揺れる‘弱さ’
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:04.80,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所詮　同じ結末
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:10.63,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そんな日常　紅霞を溶かし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:16.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}現れる陽　紅る世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:21.98,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}風になびかせ　線を引いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.11,0:01:27.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}流れるような髪先　敵を刺す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:33.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}振り斬った想い　漲る夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:38.52,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}すべては今　この手で　使命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:42.54,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}果たしてゆくだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:25.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}於是這片天空被染成紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:31.63,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再度來臨之際  唯以此身不斷向前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:48.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}擦肩而過之「人」  紛亂迷失之「物」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:53.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}終將成為  消失的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:00:59.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}熱烈震撼的「堅強」  虛無飄渺的「脆弱」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:04.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}終究是  同一結局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:10.63,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如此平凡  溶化於晚霞之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:16.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}升起的太陽  通紅的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:21.98,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}隨風飄揚  勾畫路線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.11,0:01:27.61,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}宛如飄揚的髮梢  刺向敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:33.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}揮刀斬斷的思念  瀰漫夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:42.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}一切都於此刻  僅以這雙手達成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------------------ED-----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:59.52,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}夜明け生まれ来るものよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.88,0:23:04.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}決して見失わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:09.12,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You are you　少女よ　今こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:15.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}振りほどき立ちあがれ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:36.33,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}胸の傷を隠したまま　風を切り進む君を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:41.53,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ただ見守る術など何もない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:50.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}その瞳はずっと先の　自分を探しているの?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:58.27,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}でも聞こえるよ　深い悲しみの鼓動が叫んでる!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:24:03.05,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm just　夜明け前の暗闇が
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:06.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一生を運命づける
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.41,0:24:09.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大丈夫　少女よ　今こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.77,0:24:15.37,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}悔やみ恥じることはない　Far way…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:22.97,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}十字を背負い　死ぬ気で炎を駆けろ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:59.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}拂曉降生的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.88,0:23:04.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}決不可迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:09.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You are you  少女啊  就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:15.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}掙開手站起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:36.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}隱藏著胸口的傷痕  破風前進的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:41.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}除了注視  我別無他法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:50.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你那瞳孔是否正在  探尋著前方的自我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:58.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不過我能夠聽見  你那深情悲戚的心正在吶喊著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:24:03.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm just  拂曉前的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:06.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}將此一生付為命運
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.41,0:24:09.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沒事的  少女啊  就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.77,0:24:15.37,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沒什麼好懊悔羞愧的  Far way…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:22.97,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}背負著十字架  以死的覺悟向著火焰疾走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:49.50,Optitle,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(315,240)}校舍後的宣戰通告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:01:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰莉亞露好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然囉  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為火霧戰士可是很笨的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是把在這裡看見的一大朵花當成我們的弱點了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是叫「Pinion」的磷子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}Pinion：通過泰莉亞露的自在法由人類變化而成的東西  原意為小齒輪  這裡應該是有構成「搖籃花園」的部件的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是給弄壞一朵的話  還會再開的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  泰莉亞露  快把贄殿遮那給…已經可以了吧  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  說的是啊  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那差不多該交出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰會給你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是贄殿遮那
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這裡幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:03:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  這種情況下還到處閒晃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想大概是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別出聲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是磷子的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要換地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽的到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那個  果然是那傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是以前說的另一個火霧戰士的跟班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密斯提斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道是想報恩還是迷上了那小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是不動腦子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不動腦子嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和誰在說話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小弟們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣了啊  其他的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大…大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才有沒有叫我們「小弟」？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是終於承認我們了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  比起這個快點行動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈  還不好意思吶  我純情的…嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對待方式大不一樣呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和亞拉斯托爾比起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…剛才形成的像花一樣的東西那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有像管道般不斷傳輸著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自在式仍舊混雜在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火炬沒有變化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒問你為什麼會在那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為夏娜跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許有收集存在之力的機關也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會是在花開之前就察覺到那裡有機關了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…有點感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  要想破壞那個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說基本沒可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這混亂的狀態下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然還能找到磷子的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是特別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來會發生有趣的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能幫到小鬼忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了  我的贄殿遮那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  獎勵是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜  如果派上什麼用場的話  給我獎勵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜  我呢  是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴對嘴的Kiss是像發誓一般的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些傢伙的…不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來試下刀如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想試想試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊  泰莉亞露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這刀身完全沒有波動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥喜歡用新玩具在火霧戰士身上試驗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:07:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後從皮開始到肉  骨  內臟逐一地…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽了這話不僅不惡語相向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然連哭喊都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的這個是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發誓…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帶給哥哥歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由此來滿足我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們彼此編織著愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只想著討伐的「王」的道具可沒資格說三道四的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們…只是相互依附著而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對小孩子來說這話題是不是過於高尚了點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和討伐的道具來談論愛真是毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來達成哥哥的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來保護哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩個傢伙與我和悠二…是不同的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背理  回歸順配列
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  就算再不唱歌  也不用念這麼沒情趣的咒文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,效果一樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來就是5個了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去下一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個加油站前的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遲早敵人會有所行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到處準確地破壞著Pinion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個火霧戰士到底用了什麼手段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德內
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個火霧戰士行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的記憶中可是\N「別管她  保護音樂盒」這個命令來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況有變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話搖籃花園就會崩潰的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是覺得不用管也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看中的東西不是已經到手了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊  能看穿Pinion偽裝的對手一定不能放過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正從火霧戰士手裡保護你們也是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬間燒掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是炎之劍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給自己的劍燃燒殆盡的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二會來的  悠二一定沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永別了  討伐的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人孤單的帶著燒焦的身體去另一個世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是道具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們並非共存
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是相互強烈地感受對方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從而得到力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是火霧戰士\N決心發誓履行維護世界的平衡這個使命的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之劍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是指…這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然由你先找上門來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真感激不盡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺戮的美姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說無聊的話了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點露出本性如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為野獸來享受快樂正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臨時拼湊也該適可而止吧  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼說  好好看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天將會是最後一次見到也說不定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該在這附近的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個…上面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜啊  悼詞朗誦者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼的弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悲哀啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連悔恨的感情…也已經沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束它吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少下一個好點的地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪裘莉·頓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅傷口都再生  竟然而且還阻止了那火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還回來  我的贄殿遮那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快交出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  治療哥哥的傷口和防禦你的攻擊使得力量不足了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要做到這步…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該說過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我達成哥哥的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要保護哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也感受一下這份無法抑制的感情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在有個少年在那橋上移動著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼在動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密斯提斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給打的真慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…但你也會耍些小把戲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然在這裡崩塌之前的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放出替身人偶  消除氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓別人覺得你已經死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能唱歌的狀態下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那已經是盡全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先要看看外面的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啟作  榮太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  啟作  榮太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你中招昏過去這段時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都沒回答
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下  這是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬爾克西亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是你期望的結果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怠惰的愚者——瑪裘莉·頓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都萎靡不振
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算自己是空殼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找著和別人無關的藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然變成這副樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有什麼理由向誰去抱怨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為  因為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為我戰鬥了幾百年了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追趕著銀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追趕著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算讓我稍微休息下也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這如果能被允許的話那可真幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的事情自己做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是這個世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要…想這樣振作起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要從趴在地上開始  重新來過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬爾克…這到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈  我可沒吹牛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他們說你給埋在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可沒聽到回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平安無事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔唷  榮太  接近的話可危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的大姐現在給痛打了一頓火氣正旺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是認真又認真的狀態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是  傷怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種程度就不用擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回玻璃壇去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐  紅世之徒什麼的請儘管打飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是像傻瓜一樣了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那停手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有要保護的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道裡面放了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏…夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎…是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悼…悼詞朗誦者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼  來的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.39,0:17:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰機也已成熟  真是個進攻的好時機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便士便士  便士攢起來的話就是有錢人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛…不用即興詩也不是還能打打嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是控制他們自在法的寶具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這正是操作搖籃花園的音樂盒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管如何複雜的自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要裝進去一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論多少次都可以自動使出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體…正在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的贄殿遮那還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來做薔薇的花環吧  哈！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口袋裡有好多花啊  嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋…這樣下去委託也不能完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛染兄妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是炎發灼眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明鑑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛染兄妹那樣一來也撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是先撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「千變」希德內逃跑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何事都請隨心所欲地做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都會允許的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贄殿…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊像是也搞定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那變態兄妹的自在式給我稍微做了點手腳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為像傻瓜一樣收集存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把城市復原也應該足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點  封絕馬上就要解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  不快點回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦  那就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下  悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看穿了Pinion  又找來悼詞朗誦者幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你獎勵…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.96,0:21:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.84,0:21:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真的…可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:21:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍藏的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總…總之悠二不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.28,0:22:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也對坂井同學說過「喜歡你」的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.49,0:22:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼事可以讓狡猾的小緣來妨礙的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點也不狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.58,0:22:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二是我的…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.87,0:22:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二和我在一起絕對比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.96,0:22:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該由坂井同學來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.80,0:22:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明對悠二的事一無所知的說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從現在開始就會知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.45,0:22:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.41,0:22:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能就是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.03,0:22:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會好好說出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.45,0:22:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會輸…絕對不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:22:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.00,0:24:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎發灼眼的火霧戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.65,0:24:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個和她的誕生關係密切的女性——威爾艾米娜·卡梅爾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.15,0:24:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逐漸明朗的夏娜的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.80,0:24:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  偉大之人
